videos.headline: Houston's King scampers for 46 yards
videos.description: D'Eriq King shows off his speed and bursts for 46 yards to put Houston in Tulane territory.

videos.headline: Tulane forces fumble, Catalon injured on the play
videos.description: Duke Catalon coughs up the football after a tackle and appears to injure his leg during the play.

videos.headline: Lark puts Houston in red zone with 38-yard reception
videos.description: D'Eriq King finds Courtney Lark in single coverage for a 38-yard catch at Tulane's 15-yard line.

videos.headline: Tulane's Badie escapes defenders for TD run
videos.description: Sherman Badie bounces to the outside for a 16-yard touchdown to give Tulane a 10-3 lead.

videos.headline: Tulane's Encalade breaks tackles for 45-yard reception
videos.description: Terren Encalade catches a ball from Jonathan Banks and uses his athleticism to doge defenders for a 45-yard catch and run.

videos.headline: Houston's King scrambles for TD
videos.description: D'Eriq King surveys the field and decides to scramble up the middle for a 33-yard touchdown with time expiring in the third quarter.

videos.headline: King turns on the jets to give Houston the lead
videos.description: D'Eriq King takes the snap and dashes to the outside for a 16-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
